180
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,359
Goodness! Number one again!

181
00:12:14,734 --> 00:12:16,402
You really did your best, Light!

182
00:12:16,736 --> 00:12:17,779
Well yeah.

183
00:12:18,071 --> 00:12:20,281
