a Shinigami's Notebook was real...

199
00:13:42,322 --> 00:13:47,201
but after seeing its results,
I can act with certainty.

200
00:13:48,161 --> 00:13:51,914
I see.
You've really surprised me...

201
00:13:52,582 --> 00:13:58,379
