they're from our neighbor.

233
00:15:37,019 --> 00:15:39,021
Why is it so dark in here?

234
00:15:39,439 --> 00:15:40,648
You'll ruin your eyesight!

235
00:15:40,731 --> 00:15:41,732
<i>What's going on?</i>

236
00:15:42,442 --> 00:15:44,026
<i>Mom can't see him?</i>

237
00:15:46,028 --> 00:15:49,365
That notebook...
originally belonged to me.

238
00:15:50,116 --> 00:15:55,079
And since you're the one using it,
you're the only one who can see me...

239
00:15:55,288 --> 00:15:56,456
and of course, only you...

240
00:15:56,539 --> 00:15:57,999
Can hear my voice.

241
00:15:58,332 --> 00:15:59,959
In other words,
the Death Note is a bond

242
00:16:00,042 --> 00:16:03,129
