illness or accidents.

317
00:20:35,735 --> 00:20:39,447
Then the world would truly
move in the right direction.

318
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:46,620
And I would create a new world of
earnest, kind humans.

319
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:50,624
Then you'd be the only one left...
with a bad personality.

320
00:20:51,292 --> 00:20:53,252
Huh? What're you saying?

321
00:20:53,669 --> 00:20:54,754
Ryuk...

322
00:20:55,212 --> 00:20:59,258
I'm probably the best,
most diligent honor student in Japan.

323
00:21:01,802 --> 00:21:02,970
And I...

324
00:21:05,639 --> 00:21:07,308
will become the god
of this new world!

325
00:21:10,019 --> 00:21:12,229
<i>Humans...</i>

326
00:21:13,439 --> 00:21:14,815
<i>are interesting, after all.</i>

327
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:25,493
TO BE CONTINUED

328
00:21:26,619 --> 00:21:31,624
<i>I dreamed a dream
that no one could see</i>

329
