335
00:22:02,822 --> 00:22:06,367
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

336
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:09,954
<i>To accomplish</i>

337
00:22:15,501 --> 00:22:20,965
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

338
